      "message": "nit: this code adds little value. Without this if statement, this function would panic with the message/trace that is equally useful. \n\nIMO there is no point in trying to protect from unrealistic cases. bp can be nil too, but we never check against that. What if b.Project is \"\". That\u0027s invalid build too.\n\n\n\nsame in L123-125.",
      "revId": "0202fc5bd30cedc3cd942bd8e447901a8bfa1118",
